Welcome to Portainer 3 Nodes. This email contains all the information you need to get started.

Welcome to Portainer Business Edition!

Hi Emil,

First of all, we're excited to welcome you to our community. We're here to help you get up and running with Portainer Business as quickly and easily as possible.

You've identified yourself as a home or student user so this is one of two emails that we'll send you (apart from a reminder at renewal time). We have included lots of links to resources in this email that we think you'll find really useful. After 90 days, you will be unsubscribed from our marketing emails.

Get Started Quickly

Your (3 node) license key

By now, you should have received your 3 node free license key in a separate email (please check your junk folder). If you're unable to locate your license key, please email Customer Success (mailto:success@portainer.io) .

Ensure you're on Portainer Version 2.18.4 or newer!

